---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CLEAR — Jason Ferrara">
  <article class="case-study">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <img src="/images/projects/clear-logo.png" alt="CLEAR" class="hero-logo" />
          <h1>Transforming Identity Verification into Enterprise Infrastructure</h1>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span class="meta-detail">Director, Product Design & Innovation</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">/</span>
            <span class="meta-detail">2023–Present</span>
          </div>
          <p>When I joined CLEAR, the company had enterprise ambition but no enterprise-grade infrastructure. CLEAR1 had no partner-facing console or tooling, verification completion hovered around 50%, and partner onboarding required significant internal support.</p>
          <p>I led the transformation of CLEAR1 into a scalable identity platform now serving <strong>120+ partners</strong> across healthcare, workforce, financial services, and consumer ecosystems — improving completion performance while re-architecting the console into a modular, enterprise-ready system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="device-composite">
            <div class="device device-mobile">
              <div class="device-bar">
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="device-screen">
                <div class="screen-placeholder">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <circle cx="24" cy="18" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <path d="M18 16C18 16 20 22 24 22C28 22 30 16 30 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    <rect x="14" y="32" width="20" height="6" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="42" width="28" height="2" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.15"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Verification Flow</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="device device-dashboard">
              <div class="device-bar">
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="device-screen">
                <div class="screen-placeholder">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <rect x="4" y="4" width="18" height="10" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="26" y="4" width="18" height="10" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="18" width="40" height="16" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <line x1="4" y1="24" x2="44" y2="24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
                    <line x1="4" y1="28" x2="44" y2="28" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="38" width="12" height="6" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="20" y="38" width="12" height="6" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Console Dashboard</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="device device-detail">
              <div class="device-bar">
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
                <span class="device-dot"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="device-screen">
                <div class="screen-placeholder">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <circle cx="16" cy="14" r="8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <path d="M28 8h16M28 14h12M28 20h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.5"/>
                    <line x1="4" y1="28" x2="44" y2="28" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.2"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="32" width="40" height="4" rx="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.08"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="40" width="28" height="4" rx="2" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.08"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>Verification Detail</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Study Body -->
    <div class="cs-body container">

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">Context</span>
        <h2>From airport lanes to enterprise infrastructure</h2>
        <p>CLEAR's consumer product had proven that biometric identity verification could be fast, secure, and frictionless. But the business was evolving. CLEAR1 — the enterprise platform — needed to bring that same trust model into industries with stricter regulatory requirements, more complex integration patterns, and fundamentally different user expectations. The design org needed to support both the consumer experience and a rapidly scaling enterprise product simultaneously.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">My Scope</span>
        <div class="scope-grid">
          <div class="scope-item">
            <span class="scope-key">Team</span>
            <span class="scope-val">Product design team spanning consumer and enterprise verticals</span>
          </div>
          <div class="scope-item">
            <span class="scope-key">Reporting</span>
            <span class="scope-val">Director of Product Design & Innovation, reporting to VP of Design</span>
          </div>
          <div class="scope-item">
            <span class="scope-key">Org Placement</span>
            <span class="scope-val">Central design org supporting consumer verification, enterprise console, and partner integrations</span>
          </div>
          <div class="scope-item">
            <span class="scope-key">Influence</span>
            <span class="scope-val">Cross-vertical — own design strategy across consumer, enterprise, and innovation workstreams; roadmap influence at the leadership level</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">Strategic Challenge</span>
        <h2>Two products, one identity</h2>
        <p>CLEAR's consumer product optimizes for speed — verify in seconds, move through. Enterprise partners need something different: configurability, compliance tooling, audit trails, and self-serve integration. The challenge isn't just designing for both — it's maintaining a coherent identity platform where consumer trust and enterprise rigor reinforce each other, not compete.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">Strategic Moves</span>
        <ul>
          <li>Defined a design framework spanning consumer and enterprise surfaces — shared identity patterns for enrollment, verification, and recovery that flex across contexts without fragmenting</li>
          <li>Led the enterprise console design vision, building self-serve configuration and analytics tooling that scales with partner complexity</li>
          <li>Established multi-quarter design roadmap planning in partnership with Product and Engineering, embedding design into prioritization rather than reacting to it</li>
          <li>Built design governance practices across verticals — review cadences, quality criteria, and shared component standards that maintain coherence at scale</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">Impact</span>
        <div class="metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-val">120+</span>
            <span class="metric-desc">Enterprise partners onboarded</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-val">Multi</span>
            <span class="metric-desc">Regulated industries served</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-val">2</span>
            <span class="metric-desc">Platform surfaces owned (consumer + enterprise)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>Scaled the design practice from startup-speed execution to structured multi-vertical delivery. Enterprise partners now self-serve through tooling my team designed. Consumer verification performance improved through focused iteration. The org operates with a roadmap-aligned planning cadence that didn't exist before.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <span class="cs-label">Selected Visual Evidence</span>
        <div class="visuals">
          <div class="visual">
            <img src="/images/projects/clear-tile.jpg" alt="CLEAR identity verification" />
            <span class="visual-caption">CLEAR's biometric identity verification platform spanning consumer and enterprise surfaces</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

    <footer class="cs-footer container">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to work</a>
    </footer>

  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #dbe4f0 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    height: 28px;
    width: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .meta-detail {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .meta-sep {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-copy > p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-scope {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .hero-scope li {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-scope li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.55em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-text);
  }

  .hero-stat {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .hero-stat strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Device Composite */
  .device-composite {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .device {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .device-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
  }

  .device-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  .device-screen {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .screen-placeholder {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .screen-placeholder svg {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .screen-placeholder span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .device-mobile {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
  }

  .device-mobile .device-screen {
    padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem;
  }

  .device-dashboard {
    grid-column: 2;
  }

  .device-detail {
    grid-column: 2;
  }

  /* Case Study Body */
  .cs-body {
    max-width: 48rem;
    padding-top: 4rem;
  }

  .cs-body section {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cs-body section:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cs-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-body h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Scope Grid */
  .scope-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem 2rem;
  }

  .scope-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .scope-key {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .scope-val {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* Lists */
  .cs-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cs-body li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cs-body li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.65em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Metrics */
  .metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .metric {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .metric-val {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .metric-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Visuals */
  .visuals {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .visual {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .visual img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .visual-caption {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .cs-footer {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .scope-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .metrics {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .device-composite {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
    }
  }
</style>
